## Final Verdict

The [Tapered Baguette Diamond Ring at $2,390](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/tapered-baguette-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-item-194517?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the most validated three stone setting on Blue Nile — 215 reviews, the cleanest oval-complementing silhouette, and the best art deco aesthetic at the price. Pair it with a [2ct GIA G-VS2 oval](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-search?Shape=Oval&Carats=2&Color=G&Clarity=VS2&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) for the standard [$19,870 total](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?styleIDs=three_stone&ShapeID=Oval&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational).

**For maximum finger elongation (small hands):** [Marquise Cut Three Stone by JA at $2,170](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/marquise-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-315098?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — 152 reviews, pointed tips on both ends, maximum elongating effect with an oval center.

**For pear side stones:** [Pear Sidestone Lab-Grown at $1,980](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pear-sidestone-lab-grown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-1-4-ct-tw-item-309371?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the value entry with 63 reviews; [Classic Pear Shaped Lab-Grown at $3,555](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-pear-shaped-lab-grown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-1-2-ct-tw-item-296428?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) for larger pear side stones.

**For all three ovals:** [Oval Three-Stone Diamond at $3,775](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/oval-three-stone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-1-3-ct-tw-item-192565?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) or the lab version at [$3,575](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/oval-three-stone-lab-grown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-1-ct-tw-item-309364?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational).

**For designer buyers:** Bella Vaughan's Cadillac and Moon lines start at $6,295 and go to $10,940 — purpose-built for buyers who want a recognizable designer name with a distinctive side stone geometry.

